Class ProjectRegistrationRepository

java.lang.Object
Abstract.Repository<ProjectRegistration>
ProjectRegistration.ProjectRegistrationRepository
public class ProjectRegistrationRepository extends Repository<ProjectRegistration>
Repository class for managing ProjectRegistration entities. Handles data loading and saving between CSV files and ProjectRegistration objects. Extends the generic Repository class for reusable CRUD operations.
